description:
MacGyver - Fugitive Gauntlet (2013) (digital-TPB) (Mr Norrell-Empire)


Welcome to the long-awaited return of MACGYVER, co-written by his creator! When an old friend calls for help, Mac becomes involved in in a web of industrial espionage, murder and a white-knuckle pursuit across the globe with a million dollar hit on his head and a beautiful woman by his side! Can he live long enough to save the world - or has his luck finally run out? Collects MACGYVER: FUGITIVE GAUNTLET #1-5!
